OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain throughout. Rain may be heavy and
OL,7,Fpersistent at times in the west with
OL,8,Fsome drier and brighter intervals in
OL,9,Fthe east. Breezy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain, which may be heavy
OL,13,Fin the west. Remaining cloudy
OL,14,Fovernight but becoming dry with just a
OL,15,Ffew lingering outbreaks of light rain.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with just
OL,18,Fa few outbreaks of light rain
OL,19,Fpossible. Becoming brighter and
OL,20,Flargely dry during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
