OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain at times on
OL,7,FTuesday. Wednesday will be dry with
OL,8,Fsunny spells and becoming warm. Mostly
OL,9,Fdry on Thursday with some bright or
OL,10,Fsunny intervals.
